Variable Description

Source: vignettes/variable-description.Rmd
variable-description.Rmd

Quick Reference: All Added Variables EMBRACE-II

Variable Details
age
  • Patient age at diagnosis
  • Calculation: histology_assessment_date
    • year_of_birth
  • Implementation: add_age()
  • Unit: Years
icis
  • Intracavitary/Interstitial classification
  • Calculation: Based on fraction_*_technique_tdvh columns
  • Implementation: add_icis()
  • Values: Binary (1 = ICIS, 0 = IC)
  • Note: Derived from technique values across fractions
icis_parallel_oblique
  • Detailed ICIS needle classification
  • Calculation: Based on fraction_*_technique_tdvh columns
  • Implementation: add_parallel_oblique_needles()
  • Values: “no needles”, “parallel needles”, “oblique needles”, “other”
average_nr_active_ needles
  • Average number of active needles
  • Calculation: Mean of fraction_*_active_needles columns
  • Implementation: add_average_active_needles()
  • Unit: Number of needles
time_to_bt
  • Time from EBRT start to first BT fraction
  • Calculation: fraction01date_tdvh - ebrt_start_date_tdvh
  • Implementation: add_time_to_bt()
  • Unit: Days
parametrial_involvement
  • Maximum parametrial involvement indicators
  • Implementation: add_parametrial_involvement()
  • Derived columns: Maximum values from paired measurements
  • Source pairs: BT imaging, BT exam, Diagnostic MRI, Diagnostic exam
trak_absolute
  • Total Reference Air Kerma (TRAK) values
  • Calculation: Component-wise calculation from TRAK percentages
  • Implementation: emii_add_trak_absolute()
  • Unit: cGy at 1m
  • Note: Zero values converted to NA
ott
  • Overall Treatment Time
  • Implementation: emii_add_ott()
  • Unit: Days
ott_ebrt
  • Overall treatment time of EBRT
  • Calculation: ebrt_end_date_tdvh - ebrt_start_date_tdvh
  • Implementation: add_time_to_bt()
  • Unit: Days
event_localfailure
  • Local failure event indicator
  • Calculation: Based on disease_local_status_* columns
  • Implementation: add_local_failure_event()
  • Values: 1 = failure, 0 = no failure, NA = missing
  • Note: Event triggered by status = 2 at any timepoint
event_nodalfailure
  • Nodal failure event indicator
  • Calculation: Based on disease_nodal_status_* columns
  • Implementation: add_nodal_failure_event()
  • Values: 1 = failure, 0 = no failure, NA = missing
  • Note: Event triggered by status = 2 at any timepoint
event_systemicfailure
  • Systemic failure event indicator (EMBRACE-II)
  • Calculation: Based on disease_systemic_status_* columns
  • Implementation: add_systemic_failure_event()
  • Values: 1 = failure, 0 = no failure, NA = missing
  • Note: Event triggered by status = 2 at any timepoint
event_systemic_excl_pao
  • Systemic failure event indicator (EMBRACE-I)
  • Calculation: Based on disease_systemic_status_* columns
  • Implementation: add_systemic_failure_event()
  • Values: 1 = failure, 0 = no failure, NA = missing
  • Note: Event triggered by status = 1 or 2 at any timepoint
event_vitalstatus
  • Vital status event indicator
  • Calculation: Based on vital_status and latest_assessment_date_disease
  • Implementation: add_vitalstatus_event()
  • Values: 1 = death, 0 = alive, NA = missing
  • Note: If vital status missing but assessment date exists, considered alive
timetoevent_disease
  • Time to disease event
  • Calculation: Time between histology_assesment_date and latest assessment
  • Implementation: add_time_to_diseaseevent()
  • Unit: Months
  • Note: Creates columns latest_assessment_date_disease, latest_followup_id
timetoevent_vitalstatus
  • Time to vital status update
  • Calculation: Time between histology_assesment_date and latest vital status
  • Implementation: add_time_to_last_vitalstatus()
  • Unit: Months
  • Note: Uses maximum date from all available vital status sources
time_to_bt_percent
  • Relative timing of brachytherapy
  • Calculation: time_to_bt / ott_ebrt
  • Implementation: add_time_to_bt()
  • Unit: Proportion
fraction01hrctv_ volume_bins
  • High-Risk CTV volume categories
  • Calculation: Based on fraction01hrctv_volume_tdvh
  • Implementation: add_hrctv_volume_bins()
  • Values: 0: < 30 cm³, 1: 30-45 cm³, 2: > 45 cm³, NA: missing
max_tumor_dimension_ sta_d
  • Maximum tumor dimension at diagnosis
  • Calculation: Maximum value across all tumor measurements
  • Implementation: add_max_tumor_dimension()
  • Unit: Millimeters
  • Note: Infinite values converted to NA
is_lost_to_fu
  • Lost to follow-up indicator
  • Calculation: Based on followup_*m columns
  • Implementation: add_lost_to_fu()
  • Values: TRUE/FALSE
  • Note: TRUE if any followup value = 2 at any timepoint
withdrew_consent
  • Consent withdrawal indicator
  • Calculation: Based on followup_*m columns
  • Implementation: add_lost_to_fu()
  • Values: TRUE/FALSE
  • Note: TRUE if any followup value = 3 at any timepoint
number_common_iliac_ln_ stat_d
  • Count of common iliac lymph nodes at diag.
  • Calculation: Sum of left and right common iliac lymph nodes from staging data
  • Implementation: emii_add_number_common_iliac_ln_stat_d()
  • Unit: Count
  • Note: Includes both “L com iliac” and “R com iliac” anatomical positions
number_paraaortic_ln_ stat_d
  • Count of para-aortic lymph nodes at diag.
  • Calculation: Count of lymph nodes with “Para Aortic” anatomical position from staging data
  • Implementation: add_number_paraaortic_ln_stat_d()
  • Unit: Count
  • Note: Identifies nodes specifically labeled as “Para Aortic”
